window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The best-selling novel featuring the \"wonderfully epic hero\" (<i>People</i>) who inspired the hit film <i>Jack Reacher</i>.</b> </p> <p>Skilled, stealthy, and anonymous, Jack Reacher is the perfect man for the job: to assassinate the vice president of the United States. Theoretically. The head of a high-level Secret Service security detail wants Reacher to find the holes in her system - and fast. A group of desperate men already has the vice president in its sights. And it will stop at nothing to realize its objective. </p> <p>The assassins have planned well. But they never planned on Jack Reacher. </p> <p><b>See Jack Reacher now in his first major motion picture!</b> </p>"; 
